title: X-Plane 10 Scenery, Rotterdam The Hague Airport (EHRD) V1.0
description:
Rotterdam The Hague Airport :-) Airport ICAO Code: EHRD

I hope you'll enjoy this scenery.
I converted the main buildings from FSX. 
I made this because for X-Plane there was no realistic airport for Rotterdam so far.

--Updates will follow...



Requirements:
X-Plane 10.21 or higher (PC/Mac)

These Libraries: (or newer versions)

OpenSceneryX
Ruscenery 2.1.6
CDB Library 2.2
3D People Library 3.9
flags_of_the_world (Nov 19 2013)
The Handy Objects Library 5.1
MisterX Library 1.11

Enjoy
